Please look at README.project for pcre project readme file.
----------------------------------------------------

README regarding selinux-arm project:

Quick installation:

Clean source code first:
./make clean
./make distclean

Set CC, PATH, CXX variables. 
Against the "error adding symbols: bad value" error while compiling SELinux,
-fPIC flag added CC and CXX variables in Makefile.
./configure --host=arm
./make
./make install DESTDIR=~/pcre # for custom directory installation


